<sect1 xml:id="sec.docker.docupdates.sle12_sp3_maint2">
  <title>August 2018 (Maintenance Release of &productname; 12 SP3)</title>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="sec.docker.sle_images.customizing_the_images.sles11sp4"/>, 
         updated the example to &productname; 11 SP4 (<link
         xlink:href="&bsc;1088500"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="sec.docker.portus"/>, updated the link to the upstream
         Portus documentation and removed the installation procedure, because
         Portus is now provided as a Docker image (<link
         xlink:href="&bsc;1080879"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         Switched the example application to create a &docker; container with
         from <systemitem class="daemon">postfix</systemitem> to Apache
         (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1080879"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         Improved consistency of mentions of &docker; terminology. This includes
         renaming the guide to <citetitle>&deng; Guide</citetitle>.
        </para>
       </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>
 <sect1 xml:id="sec.docker.docupdates.sle12_sp3_maint1">
  <title>July 2018 (Maintenance Release of &productname; 12 SP3)</title>

   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Portus is no longer technical preview only, hence removed
        this sentence from <xref linkend="sec.docker.portus"/> (<link
         xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1098836"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Adjusted names of base images to latest product versions (<link
         xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1050754"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>
